                  </hi>. I am a lead and glass dealer, and live at No. 4, Angel Place, Pentonville. On 18th April the prisoner brought me this order—(<hi rend="italic">Read</hi>: "Please let bearer have two lengths of nine inch pipe. William Davies, 18th April, 1857.")—Mr. Davies was a customer of mine, and I let the prisoner have the goods, having seen him once before, on April 2nd, when he also brought me an order.</p>
